Comment: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ENDING
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was right around here...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If things are going as planned, \NLuffy and the others
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,should be headed back to the dock with our gold in hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.65,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I really did forget about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.48,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize it before, but this \NWaver works in the Blue Sea, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Now we just gotta hurry back!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Onto you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,God! Buddha! I thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, whatever. Just get on already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron! I can't move like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.80,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your expressions of love are dynamic!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I collapse and literally fall in love...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.81,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've been had...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hand it to them...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna catch a fish that big!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.41,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so carefree after \Nwe nearly died trying to open it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our commander said you would appear here,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,since you had stolen the map.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cunning man.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! As strong as Luffy and Zoro are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we wait for Sanji and the others \Nto break through from outside?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our actions should already be known by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.56,0:03:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time \Nuntil reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in staying here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.17,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If the gold's not here, \Nthen let's just go look somewhere else!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like it's so easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way out is to beat these guys
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and bust down those sturdy doors!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! We gotta do what we gotta do!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Navarone, we will defeat you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp's in trouble! \NHe's helpless to do anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,End of the line, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Condoriano?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to the storage vault, \Nexactly as I expected!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?! \NWho gave you permission to open the doors?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.80,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a special inspector from Navy HQ, Major Shepherd!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With the commander's permission,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am leading a special mobile unit from headquarters.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not needed. Step back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.50,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.80,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! \NYou were the guy in jail with Usopp and Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to talk all big?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.93,0:04:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Condoriano! You managed to escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem well!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.68,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe a great deal to you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All the insults you've put me through...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.86,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's payback time for that, with interest!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Shepherd!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Things were just getting good!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking them down with that level \Nof military might is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate them...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.44,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't compare us HQ elites with you pathetic Navarone men!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We{\i0} will eliminate the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You just sit there and watch! Is that clear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm gonna crush you good, \Nso stay right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.56,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Navy HQ's very latest invention: \Na portable bazooka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Eagle Talon... the Eagle Launcher!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It packs as much punch as a warship's main cannon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They've brought out another incredible thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't scare me! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.67,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fulfill that request! Time to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Major! You have it backwards!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll get you this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell'd he come here to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty disappointing \Nfor a "special mobile unit."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Gold! Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, you guys! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you, Straw Hats! I'll get you—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape! After them!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's the gold now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Security's tighter than I thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone with Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} on a romantic night at sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the damn greatest, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.12,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn bravo, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.46,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're damn fantastic, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NIt's bon voyage, Nami—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Could you be damn quiet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.34,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the Navy is certain \Nwe're still inside the base.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.72,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But then why are they just sitting there? \NI don't like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rethink our plan somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is{\i0} there any safe place here on Navarone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The kitchen me and Sanji were at!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where loads of marines gather to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go someplace that dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.23,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. \NThe enemy might think the same thing, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's decided! \NLet's go get some food!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we're doing!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a full-fledged pirate now! \NI've grown a lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect it, no matter who comes! \NI'm a reliable man!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.38,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right! \NI wasn't lonely at all, you dummies!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Luffy and the rest not back yet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! I've been keeping watch all alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something might've happened...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Then, the gold, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.19,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My date with Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}, Part 2!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All alone again?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here, too, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure the vault was down here somewhere...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats fled into the mountains! \NComb the hills!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! No dawdling!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Major Shepherd?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.97,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I almost had them, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.64,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But finding an empty vault doesn't \Nmean they'll give up just yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.99,0:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured this might happen, \Nso the next step is already set.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I always know what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.57,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vault was a trap! \NThen where is the gold?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}think{\i0} it was around here...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. Come on already...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you just there?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.02,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The dining hall is at the far end. \NThis is the medical ward.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like there's someone here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Please do as I ask!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you are my daughter; \NI refuse to drink that nasty stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's medicine!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the doctor who acted as a hostage...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the old man!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold wasn't on your ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor in the vault.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can't believe you're father and daughter!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, old man, are you sick or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, just one swig of this \Nand I'll sleep it off like a baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.93,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a much better medicine for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! There is no drinking or \Nsmoking in the medical ward!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.31,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.86,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man! You need to listen to \Nyour daughter... no, your doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.03,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? \NAre you trying to lecture me now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.24,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I save your hides, and you \Ncome waltzing right back...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want your gold that badly, Long-nose?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do, old repair guy! \NWe're pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.29,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! These pirates worked \Nreally hard to get their stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep out of this, Kobato!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saving up money!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided that after we \Nexchange the gold for money,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna do major repairs on Merry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we can really believe a bunch of pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you don't believe me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This was our decision! \NIt's got nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.15,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all... they said that ship was their home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Home, indeed...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.21,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! It's a bit of a long way around,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.08,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but this path is unguarded, and it'll \Ntake you safely to the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This "path" is almost all cliff!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.67,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Let's go gold-hunting! \NThanks, old guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help again, old man! See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our commander's hobby is fishing, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.40,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that explains why he showed \Noff that huge fish painting!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.95,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gold is probably the \Nperfect bait to reel you in with.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.01,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, it should be \Ndangling somewhere you can see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someplace we can see it? Bait?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get going!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.11,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they do steal back the \Ngold and manage to escape,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.42,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all of Navarone will be in big trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must be crazy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.85,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no time to think up \Na plan after all, was there?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.45,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! \NAre we left to look around aimlessly for it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.38,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I heard something...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A bug? Must be my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't your imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A Waver?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you ran into Dr. Kobato...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We pretty much have no clues \Nabout where the gold is!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sit around and dawdle, \Ndawn's gonna come,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which'll make it even harder to move around.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, are there any other storage vaults?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are, they could be \Ntraps to lure us in again...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.48,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the old man \Nsaid something earlier about "bait"...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean by "something"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure, but he said...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.25,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bait to reel us in... \NIn other words, the gold is somewhere in sight!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.80,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In sight?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could "sight" be referring to a \Nplace we could imagine it being?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good thinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.14,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, who's the one dangling the bait to catch us in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Navarone's commander?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Navarone's commander is the fisherman.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.94,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the bait is near the fisherman, \Nthere's only one place it could be.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you know where the \Ncommander's room is, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead us there!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Luffy and I will go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin and the rest, get to the coast!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper's group should come to get you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Waver can only hold two people.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're gonna get spotted anyway, \Nso it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna run it at full throttle! \NYou ready?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Anytime you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.19,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They've appeared!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and find it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Up! Up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Up where, exactly?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise this is!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that vehicle?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the commander?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's the old fortress guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.90,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you would make an entrance through there!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.78,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is actually a vehicle from the sky! \NOnly Nami can ride it, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit getting excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.63,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've not met this girl before. Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.52,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you not pirates, I'd greet you \Nwarmly for your boisterous visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real shame. \NYou're perceptive and bold.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.89,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But daring can also sometimes \Nbe called recklessness.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no soldiers coming \Nto eat this time, Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.52,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But first! If there's no bait, \Nwe have nothing to bite onto!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the gold?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.65,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hidden in this room, isn't it? \NCouldn't you at least show it to us?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in front of me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.91,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is! The gold! \NNami! We finally found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fake bait, I hope?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.41,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indeed the genuine article. \NCheck for yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our gold, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go now! \NSorry for the intrusion, old fortress guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops, I think not. \NYou can't just take the bait and run.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to be too rough with the lady, now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat comes first.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat the whole lot of you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.41,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Another weird net... I'm out of strength...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat is captured!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work. Now, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not good! What do I do?! \NThere's gotta be something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, if these guys have guns, \NI do have a chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain Tempo: Sprinkler!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.06,0:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A cloud?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's forecast calls for clear skies and 0% chance of rain!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.82,0:17:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But cumulonimbus clouds may \Nsuddenly develop in some places!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch out for lightning!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, Miss?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.05,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nami...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Grab our gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.85,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not one to let prey escape \Nafter hooking it once before...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch all of you in one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Luffy?! See the ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dark to see anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Nami! A Navy ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say, it does look kind of like a warship...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are! Over here, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.19,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just let Straw Hats who were in your own room get away.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.73,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They even stole the gold. \NEven you must admit this is a grave failure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.20,0:18:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They will not escape my clutches, Major Shepherd.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.33,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You still won't admit defeat, \Nafter all that's happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I apologize. What do you say, Commander?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sit there quietly \Nand observe my leadership skills?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had already had enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened earlier was \Nsimply a minor complication!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I had already sent out my \Nspecial pirate subjugation squad,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,separate from my main unit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.85,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Then I think I will sit back \Nand watch you in action.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captain of the Pinepeak?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}will{\i0} appear near the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.65,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as planned, wait for them \Nto get drawn to it, then sink 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! \NWe're about to reach the ambush point!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! \NDo {\i1}not{\i0} let the pirate ship slip by!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute it's spotted, \Ncommence a full-scale attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of all the preparations.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to watch things from a high vantage point. \NPlace a pole in—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please not touch that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If it's about how to catch pirates, \NI can teach you anytime you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.02,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this special squadron \Nof yours on the Pinepeak?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be one more ship...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no Navarone warship.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't even look like it {\i1}is{\i0} a warship.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.73,0:20:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A warship... no, a warship-like ship... \Nis approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A Navarone ship? \NAnd what do you mean, "like"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really sure how to answer...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to smash into us!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.60,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead, Merry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.60,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the piloting! \NCouldn't have made it this far without you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch! We owe ya one!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape! After them!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.49,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.45,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! \NTo think they'd use the Pinepeak, of all things!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, you Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.53,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so aggravated. \NThey're as good as caught in a net now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Net?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At 9 p.m.{time}, the waters of \NNavarone bare their fangs,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.39,0:21:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the final... and inescapable... trap begins!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! {\i1}Now{\i0} we can escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus we got the gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's rush straight to the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, Straw Hat Luffy and his crew!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.93,0:23:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fought most valiantly against \Nthe Navy's great G8 Fortress!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done admirably, but this is the end!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it up, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Navy Fortress! \NThe Last Battle for Escape
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
