Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And whoever gets it can become Pirate King! \NIsn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
